OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FThe coach of former Sheffield United
OL,7,Fplayer Maddy Cusack called her a
OL,8,F'psycho' and was playing mind games
OL,9,Fwith her before her death, an inquest
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FChesterfield Coroners' Court heard
OL,13,FJonathan Morgan also made comments
OL,14,Fabout Ms Cusack's weight and
OL,15,Frelationship while he was the manager
OL,16,Fof United women's team, which made her
OL,17,Ffeel uncomfortable.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Cusack, aged 27, was found
OL,7,Funconscious by her father at their
OL,8,Ffamily home in Horsley, Derbyshire on
OL,9,FSeptember 2023 and she died the same
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FA fellow professional footballer Grace
OL,13,FRiglar, who played for the club at the
OL,14,Fsame time as Ms Cusack and was in
OL,15,Frelationship with her said the player
OL,16,Fwas "anxious" about Mr Morgan joining
OL,17,Fthe club in February 2023 after her
OL,18,Fexperience of working with him at
OL,19,FLeicester City years earlier.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FShe told the inquest on Tuesday: "I
OL,7,Fthink it was stuff she told me about
OL,8,Fher previous experience prior to
OL,9,FJonathan coming to Sheffield.
OL,11,F"I think she said that they played a
OL,12,Fgame against a team while Jonathan was
OL,13,Fthe manager. She had done something on
OL,14,Fthe pitch and Jonathan called her a
OL,15,Fpsycho from the sideline.
OL,17,F"I don't think she let anyone know
OL,18,Fthose types of comments affected her
OL,19,Fbut they did and they made her
OL,20,Funcomfortable."
OL,26,@nD@bOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said Mr Morgan joining United was
OL,7,Fa big stress factor for Ms Cusack.
OL,9,FMs Riglar told the court she thought
OL,10,Fthe coach made a 'personal attack' on
OL,11,Fher by not putting her in the starting
OL,12,Fline up for matches.
OL,14,FShe told the court: "She was used to
OL,15,Fstarting every game, she was an
OL,16,Fimportant member of the team. When
OL,17,FJonathan came, she was in and out from
OL,18,Fthe starting team a bit.
OL,26,@vD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,F"Her going from starting to being on
OL,7,Fthe bench quite a lot, she saw that as
OL,8,Fa setback. That impacted her a lot.
OL,10,F"I just think she almost felt like it
OL,11,Fwas a bit of a personal attack and
OL,12,Fthat Jonathan was playing mind games
OL,13,Fwith her by starting her one week and
OL,14,Fdropping her the next.
OL,16,F"She just felt those little things
OL,17,Fwere intentional."
OL,19,FMs Riglar told the inquest that Mr
OL,20,FMorgan also made comments about Ms
OL,21,FCusack's relationship with her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FWhen Mr Morgan joined United, Ms
OL,7,FRiglar said, he told the players in
OL,8,Fthe first meeting that if anyone was
OL,9,Fin a relationship within the team,
OL,10,Fthey had to tell him.
OL,12,FMs Riglar said: "She found it
OL,13,Funcomfortable when Jonathan would call
OL,14,Fme 'Mrs Cusack', especially in front
OL,15,Fof other players.
OL,17,F"We wanted to keep our relationship
OL,18,Fvery professional. The football side
OL,19,Fand relationship side were very
OL,20,Fseparate."
OL,26,@tD@QOUyD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Riglar told the court that Mr
OL,7,FMorgan made a comment about Ms
OL,8,FCusack's weight and she changed her
OL,9,Feating and exercise habits, including
OL,10,Fby not eating carbohydrates, skipping
OL,11,Fbreakfast and going for extra runs
OL,12,Fafter training.
OL,14,FMs Riglar added: "She was one of the
OL,15,Ffittest players on the team anyway."
OL,17,FThe footballer told the coroner that
OL,18,FMs Cusack had become "paranoid" at the
OL,19,Fstart of the new season.
OL,26,@vD@ROUwD@dO]zD@VOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FShe added: "She didn't really have
OL,7,Fanyone she could speak to without it
OL,8,Fgetting back to Jonathan."
OL,10,FThe inquest heard Ms Cusack had a sick
OL,11,Fnote from a doctor to have time off
OL,12,Ffootball and her marketing job at
OL,13,FUnited.
OL,15,FShe had also been prescribed anti-
OL,16,Fanxiety medication, the inquest has
OL,17,Fbeen told.
OL,26,@nD@LOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Cusack told her girlfriend before
OL,7,Fher death that she wanted to move to
OL,8,FDubai and be a flight attendant, and
OL,9,Fhad been looking for a new job online.
OL,11,FMs Riglar told the coroner: "She
OL,12,Fdidn't want to go back to playing
OL,13,Ffootball. I don't think she really
OL,14,Fknew how to get out of that situation."
OL,26,@sD@]OUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FThe Football Association began its own
OL,7,Finvestigation in January 2024, with
OL,8,Fthe governing body saying at the time
OL,9,Fthat its purpose was "to understand
OL,10,Fwhether or not any further action is
OL,11,Frequired under our jurisdiction within
OL,12,Ffootball".
OL,14,FThe FA report was shared with the
OL,15,Fcoroner a year later, but it will not
OL,16,Fbe published until the inquest has
OL,17,Fconcluded.
OL,26,@qD@VOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest, which is being heard at
OL,7,FChesterfield Coroner's Court, was
OL,8,Fpreviously postponed because of delays
OL,9,Fin disclosure of information to Ms
OL,10,FCusack's family.
OL,12,FMr Morgan was sacked by Sheffield
OL,13,FUnited in February 2024 after
OL,14,Finformation came to light about a
OL,15,Frelationship he had with a player
OL,16,Fwhile he was in charge at Leicester
OL,17,FCity.
OL,19,FHe is representing himself in the
OL,20,Finquest.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782915513
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack's head coach called her a
OL,4,C'psycho', inquest hears
OL,6,FSheffield United's own investigation,
OL,7,Fwhich concluded in December 2023,
OL,8,Ffound no evidence of wrongdoing.
OL,10,FHis dismissal was not related to the
OL,11,FFA investigation.
OL,13,FThe inquest continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
